snippet.title: Twisty Planets Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Guide your little guy 'Qub' to safely get off of each planet with the help
of some really nice touch controls.
Announcing Twisty Planets  - a new 3d puzzler from Crescent Moon and First Sight Games!

Twisty Planets is inspired by games like Qbert and the Rubik's Cube, and will launch with 3 different worlds and 60 levels. 
Portals, springs, hidden items, and more to help you along the way!
